<item>
            <title>[LU-18686] Remove dependency on Java</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18686</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Recently I had to add to build environment openjdk 1.8.0 devel as dependency, which is not supported since 2019.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;During discussion, &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=adilger&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;adilger&quot;&gt;adilger&lt;/a&gt; stated:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;My preference would be to remove the dependency on Java completely, if we can, by setting NO_JVMTI in the kernel.spec file&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="87259">LU-18686</key>
            <summary>Remove dependency on Java</summary>
                <type id="4" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11310&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Improvement</type>
